gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 110, Jazz 102
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeat the Jazz, 110-102. Nikola Jokic led the way with 27 points, 11 assists, and 10 rebounds for the Nuggets, while Aaron Gordon added 21 points, seven rebounds, and two assists in the victory. Lauri Markkanen tallied 27 points, 14 rebounds, and five assists for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 4-0 on the season, while the Jazz fall to 1-3.
